Package: PTMSignalR
Type: Package
Title: Integrate Post-Translationnal Modifications to infer Ligand-Receptor Interactions
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jacques","Colinge",email="jacques.colinge@inserm.fr",role="aut",comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2466-4824")),
    person("Pierre","Giroux",email="girouxpierre3@gmail.com",role="cre",comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-3142-318X")))
Description: BulkSignalR extension. Integration of post-translational modifications (PTMs) for inference of ligand-receptor (LR) interactions.
    BulkSignalR bases its inferences
    on the LRdb database included in our other package, SingleCellSignalR
    available from Bioconductor. It relies on a statistical model that
    is specific to bulk data sets. Different visualization and data
    summary functions are proposed to help navigating prediction results.
URL: https://github.com/girouxpierre/PTMSignalR
BugReports: https://github.com/girouxpierre/PTMSignalR/issues
